- `type(text)` - Type the given text
- `scroll(direction)` - Scroll up/down/left/right
- `hotkey(key1, key2, ...)` - Press hotkey combination (e.g., ctrl, c)
- `wait(seconds)` - Wait for specified seconds
- `done()` - Task completed

## Guidelines
